pycsd is a set of functions that can be used to calculate the current
source density in neural tissue.  The proceedure is published in

Pettersen et. al, "Current-source density estimation based on inversion of 
eletrostatic forward solution" 
Journal of Neuroscience Methods 154 (2006) 116-133


